name: Mysis
tagline: Analysis for the paper Johnson et.al.
body:
### This is the homepage for the analyses in Johnson et. al. .
This website contains code and model statements for the analysis in Johnson et. al. This site is intended to be a reference for the analysis done in the manuscript and also tutorial for future model development

[results](https://github.com/jtipton25/mysis/_posts/2016-01-12-Appendix.md)
